<body>
  <p>
      Rev your engines for the <b>Robot Races!</b><br />
      In teams of 3-4 you will <b>design and build</b> a <b>super-robot</b> in <b>LEGO MINDSTORMS</b> that will <b>race</b> against the others in a <b>3-lap loop</b> around the game studio.<br />
      Robots <b>must pass several marked checkpoints</b> along the path to be considered eligible for the next lap.<br />
      The race commences in Session [x]
  </p>

  <b>Learning Objectives:</b>

  <ul>
      <li><b>Plan</b> a remote-controlled robot, with an aptitude for <b>moving supah-fast</b> and optionally <b>weapon(s) to obstruct other racers</b></li>
      <li>Use the <b>agile development philosophy</b> to build and program the robot components within your group</li>
      <li>Be the <b>very best</b> like <b>no-one ever was</b></li>
  </ul>

  <b>Agenda:</b>

